<note n="0205001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205001">明闇＝眼間【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0205002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205002">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0205003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205003">加＝跏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0205004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205004">遍＝偏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0205005" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205005">以＝少【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0205006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0205006">自＝白【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
